data.text: (ג) The works of the Lord are great,
(ה) His work is honourable and glorious:
(ז) He hath made his wonderful works to be remembered:
(ט) He hath given meat unto them that fear him:
(כ) He hath shewed his people the power of his works,
(מ) The works of his hands are verity and judgment;
(ס) They stand fast for ever and ever,
(פ) He sent redemption unto his people:
(ר) The fear of the Lord is the beginning of wisdom:
